title: Journey to the Unknown
description: This is a series of stories relating the adventures of Emett and Alison as they become accomplished warrior and sorceress. They have to learn those trades to become the rulers of the magical land called Magicktopia.Journey to the Unkown- Book 1Emett and Alison, a couple of highschool seniors, get flipped by magic to a land plagued by demons, mad wizards, and vile sorceresses. They must learn to be a champion warrior and an exceptional sorceress so that they can become the rulers of the magical land of Magicktopia. Join them as they fight for their lives and the lives of the good people around them.
author: Jaclyn Cadell
